    {
      "id": "script-scope-test-steps",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Test Steps",
      "position": {
        "x": 1080,
        "y": 620
      },
      "width": 420,
      "height": 260,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Test Steps\n\n1. Bind a local script to `Scope Probe Script`.\n2. Run `api.getNodes()` before expansion and note the count.\n3. Expand `Expand Script Scope Root`.\n4. Focus the root fragment and rerun the script: expanded-fragment nodes should stay out of scope.\n5. Focus a node in the expanded fragment and rerun: scope should switch to that fragment.\n6. Try `api.getNode()` or `api.updateNode()` against a foreign-fragment node id and confirm the diagnostics surface reports a scope error.",
        "memo": "",
        "link": "",
        "isRoot": false,
        "root": false,
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
