    {
      "id": "script-scope-test-create-instruction",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Create / Refocus Test Steps",
      "position": {
        "x": 1160,
        "y": 1540
      },
      "width": 520,
      "height": 280,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Create / Refocus Test Steps\n\n1. Expand `Expand Script Scope Root`.\n2. Click a node inside the expanded fragment so it becomes focused.\n3. Run `Create Local Node Test`.\n4. Confirm a new node appears in the expanded fragment.\n5. Click back into the host fragment.\n6. Run `Read Created Node From Host Test`.\n7. Expect a scope error.\n8. Focus the expanded fragment again and confirm the created node is still there.\n",
        "memo": "",
        "link": "",
        "isRoot": false,
        "root": false,
        "_classBinding": {
